{
  "texts": [
    "Different countries have started to identify how to deal with this problem.",
    "For example, in Australia, the Department of Education of three state governments, i.e., New South Wales, Victoria and Queensland, have announced that they will ban ChatGPT in schools.",
    "A similar decision has been taken in New York City public schools [61,62,63].",
    "In other words, using GAI is still banned in the education sector of many countries because the concerns have not been addressed yet.",
    "Undoubtedly, these policies and regulations will not last forever."
  ]
}